      <title>Janus Henderson 押注仍然便宜的日本金融股</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/janus-henderson-bets-on-still-cheap-japanese-financial-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Janus Henderson Investors 的一位投资组合经理表示，尽管日本金融公司在过去一年稳步增长，但它们的价值仍然被低估，而且股息支付不断增加使其成为一项不错的投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/janus-henderson-bets-on-still-cheap-japanese-financial-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 01:13:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
